{
  "stem": "19242.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then the next time you said, well, I've been here twice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why don't you get him once?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I mean, everybody, even if you don't want it, you had to do it though.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that's the close call I had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You were cut off from the world.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You only-- a lot of-- some of them could escape into town and check up on things what goes on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And not-- the Gentile could do it though.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, to Miedzyrzecz because they are Gentile.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, they recognized who was-- who was Jewish and who not.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Poles, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were no Poles altogether.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one time, we had, like, two of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they did go out for some mission, and it didn't come through.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they think maybe they turned them in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, they said to them, they don't want them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You have 48 hours.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Find yourself another group.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, they didn't punish them or anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were-- didn't enough proof.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they tell them, there's other groups over here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Probably there was more than one, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they tell them to hook up with another group.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just a plain gun, a single bullet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like you're here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Over here you've got-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Hunting-- hunting-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A single bullet gun, you pull the- the trigger in it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we had-- we thought we did, but I didn't go back to check out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think we on one mission was successful.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We could pick up a couple of guns with that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And later, I hear that it-- that it was so many.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was hard to prove it [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
